元以\r\n下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPHM/110%2c%e9%87%8d%e4%b8%8a%e6%9b%b4%e4%b8%80%2c59%2c20220802%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,110,重上更一,59,20220802,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"重上更一","JNO":"59","JDATE":"20220802","JTITLE":"貪污治罪條例等"}